thread.title: Jeff Hofstra
thread.title_full: Wilson Amplifiers reviewed by Jeff Hofstra

author: Jeff Hofstra
title: Jeff Hofstra
text: I was hopeful that the technology had improved from the past cell phone boosters. But to my surprise it hasn't. By the time I was able to test out the strength of the WeBoost I was disappointed. Also out of the return date. It may work better for some but not in my case, sorry to say.
